Exactly 1 year ago, I launched #Bitcoin Backstage alongside @BitcoinMagazine. It was a project that's sole purpose was to build a bridge between the bitcoin community and the normies, making the trending topics more digestible. 

As I watch the first couple of episodes, all I can think is how much we have grown, how we have improved, and how much love, sweat and tears have gone to this project. 

Andrea and I launched this project PEAK bear market, with all the odds against us. To those that are creating or want to start something but are waiting for the right moment, let me tell you something: the perfect moment DOES NOT exist. 

Launch your project NOW. Perfect it along the way. Get feedback. Evolve. But STOP waiting for the "right moment" because that moment will never come. 

In order to make you 52 episode, you need to make your first. 

So, thank you for those that watch the show and have been following. And thank you bitcoin magazine for allowing me to produce, host and publish BBS🧡🥹

@Dmailofficial, a cutting-edge Web3 platform, is transforming the decentralized finance (#DeFi) landscape by harnessing the power of Bitcoin (#BTC) and its robust security features. 

As BTCFi (Bitcoin Finance) gains traction, Dmail is poised to play a vital role in unlocking Bitcoin's full potential in DeFi.

𝐁𝐓𝐂𝐅𝐢: 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐍𝐞𝐱𝐭 𝐁𝐢𝐠 𝐓𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐠

Following the success of Ordinals and Runes, BTCFi is emerging as a significant development in the blockchain space. By leveraging Bitcoin's security and trust, BTCFi can provide decentralized financial products, offering a robust alternative to Ethereum-based DeFi solutions.

𝐊𝐞𝐲 𝐓𝐞𝐜𝐡𝐧𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐠𝐢𝐞𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐈𝐧𝐟𝐫𝐚𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞𝐬-

Dmail's development relies on several key technologies and infrastructures, including:

▪️Layer 2 Solutions: Enhancing Bitcoin's scalability and transaction efficiency.

▪️Smart Contract Integration: Unlocking DeFi applications on Bitcoin.

▪️Decentralized Identifiers (DIDs): Ensuring secure and private user authentication.

▪️Interoperability Protocols: Fostering collaboration between Bitcoin and other blockchain networks.

𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐄𝐓𝐇 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐁𝐓𝐂 𝐄𝐜𝐨𝐬𝐲𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐬 

Dmail bridges the gap between the ETH and BTC ecosystems, leveraging the strengths of both:

◾️Ethereum: Robust smart contract capabilities, strong support for dApps, DeFi projects, and NFTs.

◾️Bitcoin: Unparalleled security, stability, and widespread adoption as a digital gold standard.

Hükümetlerin #Bitcoin satışları bence biraz abartılıyor. 

Son günlerde Almanya ve ABD hükümetlerinin Bitcoin satışları, yatırımcılar üzerinde büyük bir satış baskısı yarattı ve Bitcoin'in %10'dan fazla düşmesine neden oldu. Ancak, CryptoQuant CEO'su Ki Young Ju, bu satışların etkilerinin abartıldığını belirtiyor. Hükümetlerin elindeki BTC, toplam gerçekleşmiş piyasa değerinin sadece %4'ünü oluşturuyor.

Gerçekleşmiş piyasa değeri, piyasaya giren toplam sermayeyi ölçer. Bu değer üzerinde hükümet satışlarının etkisi oldukça sınırlı.

Young Ju, Bitcoin boğa döngüsünün önümüzdeki yılın başına kadar devam edeceğini öngörüyor ve spot traderlara fiyatların 47.000 dolara kadar düşebileceği uyarısında bulunuyor. 

On-chain veriler, Bitcoin sahiplerinin %82'sinin şu anki fiyatlarda kârda olduğunu gösteriyor. Büyük işlemler ve kurumsal yatırımcı ilgisi yüksek seviyelerde seyrediyor. Borsalardaki alım talebi, satış baskısından daha güçlü ve bu da fiyatların toparlanmasına yol açabilir.

Moeda digotal , controle absoluto !

Até 2030, a moeda digital do banco central (CBDC) dominará a economia global, trazendo uma revolução sem precedentes. Sob o controle do sistema financeiro centralizado, cada transação será monitorada com rigor, prometendo segurança e transparência, mas ao custo da liberdade individual.Neste novo mundo, a ideia de possuir algo se tornará uma memória distante. Com a CBDC, a sociedade será encorajada a usar bens e serviços sem a necessidade de propriedade. "Você não terá nada e será feliz", dizem, enquanto o controle do sistema dita as regras do jogo.Essa transformação dramática visa criar uma sociedade mais sustentável e equitativa, onde a felicidade não depende da posse, mas sim das experiências. No entanto, à medida que o controle do sistema se intensifica, a linha tênue entre segurança e privacidade se torna cada vez mais nebulosa, desafiando nossa noção de liberdade. Isso não vai ser bom.

cleaned_data.original_text:
Rumors are circulating that Trump will announce a #Bitcoin strategic reserve in the USA if/when he is elected. 

While a move to back the dollar with #BTC would result in massive buying pressure from the juggernaut that is the USA, it would probably cause many other nations to follow suit as well. 

The result? A stampede of nation states rushing to hoard the scarcest asset known to man.

While I always envisioned a bottom-up path to hyperbitcoinization, led by the plebs, we might get the exact opposite...top-down adoption perpetuated by game theory at the nation-state level. 

But here's why I love Bitcoin so much. 👇

Let's say that nation states don't ever back fiat with #BTC. Great. That simply means fiat will collapse even sooner. #Bitcoin still wins because....

All roads lead to Bitcoin.

cleaned_data.original_text:
🎓 #MonkVersity Understanding BIP-420: A Step Towards Bitcoin’s Evolution

Raise your hand if you know what OP_CAT and BIP-420 are? 
BIP stands for - Bitcoin Improvement Protocol.
There’s some cool innovation happening in Bitcoin land that’s worth reviewing. The story starts all the way back in 2010—that’s like a century in crypto time! 😁

📜 A Bit of History:
➯ Shortly after Bitcoin was founded, there existed an OP code called OP_CAT.
➯ OP_CAT allowed building smart contract-type functionality on Bitcoin.
➯ It generated a lot of discussion and excitement but was ultimately decided to removed the code.
➯ The removal was due to security risks, specifically DDoS attacks.
➯ This decision was made by Satoshi Nakamoto.
➯ OP_CAT has been shelved ever since.

👼 The Revival: BIP-420
➠ Over a decade later, the Bitcoin ecosystem has significantly evolved.
➠ Innovations such as:
  ➛ Ordinals: Enable digital art and collectibles on Bitcoin.
  ➛ BRC-20 tokens: Introduce fungible tokens to the Bitcoin network.
  ➛ Taproot upgrade: Enhances privacy and scripting capabilities.
➠ Resurged interest in OP_CAT has led to its new incarnation: **BIP-420**.

📝 BIP-420 Proposal:
 ➥ Aims to reintroduce the OP_CAT code through a proposed soft fork.
➥ Allows the combination of two stack elements into one.
 ➥ Enables more complex Bitcoin scripting capabilities akin to basic smart contract functionality.

🎯 Potential Impacts of OP_CAT:
➼ Layer 2 Solutions: Facilitate the building of advanced Layer 2 solutions.
➼ Complex Scripts: 
  ➢ Secure vaults.
  ➢ Decentralized key exchanges.
➼ Enhanced Functionality: 
  ➢ Broadens Bitcoin’s use cases.
  ➢ Brings Bitcoin closer to Ethereum’s smart contract capabilities.

🛠️ Starkware’s Contribution:
➙ Announcement: Starkware plans to introduce STARKS to the Bitcoin ecosystem once OP_CAT is implemented.
➙ Unified Layer 2: Creating a unified Layer 2 across EVM (Ethereum Virtual Machine) and Bitcoin.
➙ Sponsorship: Starkware is sponsoring $1M in research to explore the pros and cons of OP_CAT.
This underscores the potential impact and importance of BIP-420 in the crypto landscape.

⚒️ Dynamic’s Contribution
➜ Commitment: We are committed to contributing to this evolving landscape through innovative projects.
➜ BitcoinKit:
   Designed to empower developers with tools to build sophisticated applications on Bitcoin.
  ⟶ Leverages advancements proposed by BIP-420.

🏁 Conclusion:
» Potential: BIP-420 could unlock significant innovation within the Bitcoin ecosystem.
» Adoption Timeline: Adoption might take time, considering the stakes involved in Bitcoin.
» Future Outlook:
  › This proposal could lead to significant advancements and new possibilities for Bitcoin.
  › Anticipate more companies and initiatives emerging if this OP code gets closer to reality.

BIP-420 is a promising development that can push Bitcoin towards new horizons, enabling functionalities that could rival those of Ethereum. Its successful implementation could pave the way for a new era of innovation and use cases for the grandfather of crypto.

#Bitcoin #BTC #ETH $ORDI $MUBI #Ordinals #CryptoEducation

Fibonacci Ratios can be used more than just for price, here I've applied them to time for #Bitcoin.

When we draw our retraces at the halvings, we get near-perfect first and second cycle top date predictions for the past 2 cycles at the red .236 and orange .382.

The first cycle works as well, but only when the retrace is drawn starting in April 2012 strangely.

The retraces also give us close dates for the cycle bottom (.618) and the first early top (.786).

Our next halving is projected to be on March 24th, 2028. Here are the upcoming important dates with that information:

First Top - March 2025

Final Top - October 2025

Bear Market Halfway Point - April 2026

Bear Market Bottom - September 2026

First Early Top - May 2027

DD ile Uzun Vadeli Bitcoin Analizi 1

$BTC

3 Günlük grafik;

- Beyaz çizginin kaybı sonrası fiyatın mavi kutuya gitmesini bekliyorum, orada yaşanılacak ve tahminimce q3 ortalarına denk gelecek  global ekonomik esnemeler sonucunda #bitcoin tarafında yeni bir bullrun bekliyorum.

Önemli koşul fiyatın mavi kutudayken pozitif haberler ile fiyatlanması.

$BTC 

Günlük grafik;

- Anlık olarak direnç bölgesinden bir red yedi (kırmızı kutu). Eğer kırmızı kutunun kazanımı gerçekleşirse fiyatın bir sonraki hedef noktası, öncelikle EQ seviyesi ardından üst kırmızı kutu olacağını düşünüyorum. En üstte bulunan kırmızı kutu kazanılırsa yeni en yüksek #Bitcoin fiyatını göreceğimizi düşünüyorum.

Önemli koşul fiyatın kırmızı kutuyu kazanması.

Düşük bakiyeye sahip kullanıcılar için, yüksek sermaye fırsatı.

Kripto varlıklarda aldığım işlemleri, @BemFunding  üzerinden de oluşturuyorum.
480$ ödeyerek aldığım 100.000$'lık hesabım 2 günde neredeyse 6000$ karda.
Aşamaları tamamladıktan sonra bu hesaptan yapacağım çekimi dağıtacağım ve süreci videolandıracağım.

Fon firmalarının ne olduğunu bilmiyorsanız videoyu izleyebilirsiniz ; https://t.co/1e3pAfJtWV

Başarılar.

Earn $WTF with the $WTF Slot Game, releasing Wednesday @ 7am PST (7/17), and the $WTF Sale starts tomorrow @ 7am PST (7/16)

Introduction
Welcome to our unique Rune distribution experience! At Frucks, we believe in doing things differently and having fun along the way. Instead of a simple random airdrop, we've created an engaging experience that embodies the spirit of our Ordinal project.

Introducing the $WTF Slots game—a daily interaction designed to excite the ordinal community and get everyone pumped about our Rune.

Below we will run through how to earn $WTF step by step.

Getting Started
Who can play to earn?
* Holders of a FrucksBTC Ordinal
* Holders of a partner Ordinal project
* Winners of whitelist (WL) spots from various giveaways
* Participants in the $WTF Sale
Note: The Frucks team won't dictate how you should hold or distribute your tokens to participate. Prepare in your own way!

The entire experience will be hosted on our website.

Gameplay Mechanics
1. Connect your wallet
2. Spin as many times as you are allowed (participate in the sale to get up to 6 per day)
3. Earn points
4. Rank Up
5. Come back the next day!
Note: The goal is to get as many points as you can during the experience - this will last about one week from launch until all available $WTF is earned.

Access Types and Perks
Frucks Holders
* Automatic access to play
* Big Multiplier per Fruck held
* 6x spins (per day)
* Frucks Holder Airdrop

Partner Ordinal Projects
* The entire collection gains access to play
* Multiplier per token held
* 3x spins (per day)

WL Access
* Access to play
* 3x spins (per day)

Sale Access - Fruck Genie
* Sale Airdrop Allocation
* 3x spins daily (per day)
* 6x spins daily (per day)
* Access to earn if not already WL
Note: The more BTC deposited, the higher piece of the allocation you will receive. There is no limit to depositing, but there is a maximum of 6 spins daily across players!

* Earn Points: Play the slots to earn points
* Leaderboard: Points determine your rank and position on the leaderboard
* Ranks: Different ranks require specific points and offer varying amounts of $WTF
- Iron
- Bronze
- Silver
- Gold
- Platinum
- Diamond
- Fruck
- Big Fruck
- Grand Fruck
- King Fruck
Note: All earned $WTF will be determined by a ranking system and distributed by the Frucks team. This will be an airdrop to all participants.

Good Luck!

𝐖𝐓𝐅 𝐢𝐬 𝐁𝐥𝐨𝐜𝐤𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐢𝐧 𝐈𝐧𝐝𝐞𝐱𝐢𝐧𝐠?! 🤔 

An indexer's job is to process and organize the raw data created on-chain, into a format that's easily accessible and understandable, and then create structured databases that can be queried efficiently by developers so dApps and services can be built and maintained. 🗄️

For example, just think about your favourite web3 marketplace, exchange, game, analytics dashboard etc….the data on those sites is provided by indexers.👌 

HOWEVER, on Bitcoin, 99.9% of indexers are centralised, so as it stands, we all have to just trust their version(s) of ‘the truth’! 👀 

 ....."𝘵𝘳𝘶𝘴𝘵 𝘶𝘴 𝘣𝘳𝘰, 𝘸𝘦 𝘸𝘰𝘯'𝘵 𝘤𝘩𝘢𝘯𝘨𝘦 𝘰𝘳 𝘮𝘢𝘯𝘪𝘱𝘶𝘭𝘢𝘵𝘦 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘥𝘢𝘵𝘢, 𝘸𝘦 𝘱𝘳𝘰𝘮𝘪𝘴𝘦!" 😬

At this point, you should pause for a second and ask yourself this one question: 🔽 

What was the point of Satoshi creating such a perfectly decentralised data creator like Bitcoin, if we then have to trust one company’s interpretation of that data?! 🙈

This is why 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐜 𝐂𝐨𝐫𝐞 from @trac_btc is SO vital! 🙏

It is #Bitcoin’s fully decentralised indexer, and it will make on-chain data reliably accessible through its thousands of distributed validator nodes, that MUST first reach consensus, similarly to Bitcoin when it creates the raw data. 🤝

Importantly, those who run validator nodes on their device, and help to support the decentralisation of the Trac network, will be rewarded with token APY! 🪙

Just like for those who run Bitcoin nodes, if you contribute to the decentralisation of the Trac network, you should be rewarded! 🙌

Decentralised indexers are one of the most fundamentally important pieces of infrastructure within a blockchain ecosystem, and they play a crucial role in fostering a scalable and secure ecosystem for blockchain-based economies to thrive and grow! 📈

𝐑𝐞𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐞𝐫:
If you'd like to own/run your own Trac Validator Node, we are currently running regular rounds, with 300 Validator Licences purchasable per round, and with increasing price points. 📈

Follow @trac_btc to stay up to date with the sales rounds in the coming weeks and months 🔔

4. “I will also sign an executive order directing the IRS to treat Bitcoin as an eligible asset for 1031 exchange into real property”

cleaned_data.original_text:
Is #Bitcoin due for a new high in August?

When you put aside the fact that March 2024 made new  ATHs 1 year earlier than usual and just look at time, the Halving Cycles Theory comes right back into view.

Every major high we see in each year Orange, Green, Blue, or Red has a double that I call an echo high.

The echo highs for Blue Year have come in January and February. March falls perfectly in range.

If that's true, it means we're still due for a second early top (solid purple dot).

August has been seen twice as a month for second early tops in 2012 and 2020, and that month is just around the corner.

Keeping watch
